Module de.sft.mq.rc
Package de.s42.mq.fonts.fnt.parser

Interface FntParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
FntLoader, FntParserBaseListener
public interface FntParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by FntParserParser.
